config BR2_PACKAGE_RTL8812EU
    bool "rtl8812eu"
    depends on BR2_LINUX_KERNEL
    depends on !BR2_s390x
    help
      Realtek RTL8812AU/EU USB Wi-Fi driver (aircrack-ng v5.6.4.2 fork)
      with monitor mode and frame injection. Used by WFB-ng on the
      lite agent radio pair.

      The recipe carries a provisional cfg80211 compat shim patch
      (0001-luckfox-bsp-cfg80211-shim.patch). The hunk lands on the
      first `make rtl8812eu-source` once the upstream tree is on disk
      and the exact line numbers in os_dep/linux/ioctl_cfg80211.c can
      be confirmed against the Luckfox 5.10 BSP. Until then the patch
      is a documented placeholder; the build emits a benign warning
      when the placeholder hunk is applied.
